{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"2cae6f12-7f78-4074-9d5a-41316b7401e3","content":"Here's my analysis of **evaluation performance issues** in `EvalHeavy.csproj`:\n\n---\n\n### 1. 🔴 File I/O Property Function (Line 13)\n```xml\n<BuildNotes>$([System.IO.File]::ReadAllText('build-notes.txt'))</BuildNotes>\n```\n**Problem:** Property functions that perform file I/O execute during *evaluation* (before any targets run). This blocks the evaluation phase with disk access and runs on every single evaluation — including IDE background evaluations.\n\n**Fix:** Move file reading to a target with `Inputs/Outputs` so it only runs at build time when needed.\n\n---\n\n### 2. 🟠 Broad Glob Pattern (Line 9)\n```xml\n<AdditionalFiles Include=\"**\\*.*\" Exclude=\"**\\bin\\**;**\\obj\\**\" />\n```\n**Problem:** `**\\*.*` walks the entire directory tree during evaluation. If `node_modules`, `.git`, or other large directories exist, this becomes extremely expensive. Only `bin`/`obj` are excluded.\n\n**Fix:** Add large directories to `DefaultItemExcludes` or narrow the glob to specific extensions/paths.\n\n---\n\n### 3. 🟡 Deep Import Chain (3 levels)\n```\nEvalHeavy.csproj → level1.props → level2.props → level3.props\n```\n**Problem:** Each import adds evaluation overhead. While 3 levels is moderate, this pattern can grow quickly. In real projects with deeply nested imports (>20 levels), evaluation stalls significantly.\n\n**Note:** Currently manageable but watch for growth.\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n| Issue | Severity | Fix |\n|-------|----------|-----|\n| `File::ReadAllText` in property | High | Move to a build target |\n| `**\\*.*` glob | Medium-High | Narrow scope or exclude more dirs |\n| Nested imports (3 deep) | Low | Monitor; flatten if it grows |\n\nThe file I/O property function is the most impactful issue — it forces synchronous disk reads on every evaluation, including IDE design-time builds.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c17c2966-e92f-4028-8f81-f59b012e2de4","outputTokens":502,"requestId":"0416:71A4F:BD03C0:D9C5AC:69F2AE46"},"id":"3af2d1ed-8da6-49ca-b291-98e5cb18beb8","timestamp":"2026-04-30T01:20:19.286Z","parentId":"9d533f29-1dd9-4994-aa8c-95a0e7165275"}
